OL,3,C'No surprise, just disappointment,'
OL,4,Csay Brown family over Benn inquiry
OL,5,Cappeal
OL,7,FThe family of Sean Brown has branded
OL,8,Fthe government's decision to seek
OL,9,Fleave for a Supreme Court appeal in
OL,10,Fthe case, as a disgrace.
OL,12,FIn April, a court ruled that the
OL,13,Fgovernment was acting unlawfully in
OL,14,Frefusing to order an inquiry into the
OL,15,FGAA official's murder by loyalist
OL,16,Fparamilitaries in 1997.
OL,18,FThe case is expected to go before The
OL,19,FCourt of Appeal again on Friday.
