OL,3,C'No surprise, just disappointment,'
OL,4,Csay Brown family over Benn inquiry
OL,5,Cappeal
OL,7,FThe Secretary of State Hilary Benn has
OL,8,Fnot confirmed he ultimately intends to
OL,9,Ftake the case to the Supreme Court,
OL,10,Fbut applied for "protective leave" to
OL,11,Fappeal to the UK's highest court if he
OL,12,Fbelieves that course of action to be
OL,13,F"necessary".
OL,15,FFirst Minister Michelle O'Neill
OL,16,Fbranded the move "cruel and inhumane"
OL,17,Fwhile the Taoiseach said the Brown
OL,18,Ffamily had already been waiting "far
OL,19,Ftoo long" for answers.
