OL,7,FMr Benn has also applied to the Court
OL,8,Fof Appeal in Belfast for further time
OL,9,Fto consider its judgment in the Brown
OL,10,Fcase.
OL,12,FHe has indicated the outcome of that
OL,13,Fapplication, and what transpires
OL,14,Fduring any subsequent extension, if
OL,15,Fone is granted, will determine his
OL,16,Fdecision-making in respect of a
OL,17,FSupreme Court challenge.
