OL,3,C'No surprise, just disappointment,'
OL,4,Csay Brown family over Benn inquiry
OL,5,Cappeal
OL,7,FMr Brown, 61, the chairman of Bellaghy
OL,8,FWolfe Tones GAA club in Co
OL,9,FLondonderry, was ambushed, kidnapped
OL,10,Fand murdered by loyalist
OL,11,Fparamilitaries as he locked the gates
OL,12,Fof the club in May 1997.
OL,14,FNo-one has ever been convicted of his
OL,15,Fkilling.
OL,17,FPreliminary inquest proceedings last
OL,18,Fyear heard that in excess of 25 people
OL,19,Fhad been linked by intelligence to the
OL,20,Fmurder, including several state agents.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/15
