OL,3,C'No surprise, just disappointment,'
OL,4,Csay Brown family over Benn inquiry
OL,5,Cappeal
OL,7,FIt had also been alleged in court that
OL,8,Fsurveillance of a suspect in the
OL,9,Fmurder was temporarily stopped on the
OL,10,Fevening of the killing, only to resume
OL,11,Fagain the following morning.
OL,13,FLast month, three judges at the Court
OL,14,Fof Appeal in Belfast said the
OL,15,FGovernment's failure to order a public
OL,16,Finquiry into the murder "cannot stand"
OL,17,Fand gave Mr Benn four weeks to
OL,18,F"reflect upon the judgment".
