OL,3,C'No surprise, just disappointment,'
OL,4,Csay Brown family over Benn inquiry
OL,5,Cappeal
OL,7,FOutside the Court of Appeal, Mr
OL,8,FBrown's 87-year-old widow Bridie had
OL,9,Fissued a plea to Mr Benn not to
OL,10,Fchallenge judgment at the Supreme
OL,11,FCourt in London.
OL,13,FHowever, the Northern Ireland
OL,14,FSecretary has now taken steps to give
OL,15,Fhimself that option.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/15
