OL,3,C'No surprise, just disappointment,'
OL,4,Csay Brown family over Benn inquiry
OL,5,Cappeal
OL,7,FReacting to the move, Mrs Brown said:
OL,8,F"I pleaded directly with Hilary Benn
OL,9,Fnot to be appealing Sean's case to the
OL,10,FSupreme Court in London, that he
OL,11,Fshould do what the courts have told
OL,12,Fhim to do.
OL,14,F"He has refused my plea. I'm not
OL,15,Fsurprised but I am bitterly
OL,16,Fdisappointed."
OL,18,FShe added: "I am now terrified as to
OL,19,Fwhat secrets the British government
OL,20,Fare hiding. It seems we just don't
OL,21,Fcount."
