OL,4,Csay Brown family over Benn inquiry
OL,5,Cappeal
OL,7,FShe added: "It's totally disgraceful.
OL,8,FWe were distraught at the fact that
OL,9,Fthis information had been released
OL,10,Fwithout the family knowing entirely.
OL,11,FYes, some of us had received it (legal
OL,12,Fletter sent to the family's
OL,13,Fsolicitor), but the rest of us were at
OL,14,Fwork. We didn't get that information
OL,15,Fstraight away and to suddenly hear it
OL,16,Fbeing broadcast is disgraceful.
