OL,3,C'No surprise, just disappointment,'
OL,4,Csay Brown family over Benn inquiry
OL,5,Cappeal
OL,7,F"And, again, it's just another thing
OL,8,Fthat the Government are trying to do
OL,9,Fto undermine us as a family and treat
OL,10,Fus with so much disrespect, which has
OL,11,Fhappened right through the 28 years
OL,12,Fsince my father was murdered."
OL,14,FMr Brown's daughter said the only
OL,15,Facceptable way forward for her family
OL,16,Fwas a public inquiry.
