OL,3,C'No surprise, just disappointment,'
OL,4,Csay Brown family over Benn inquiry
OL,5,Cappeal
OL,7,F"There's obviously very dirty secrets
OL,8,Fthere that the Government want to keep
OL,9,Ffrom us as a family and they're going
OL,10,Fout right, taking all action that they
OL,11,Fpossibly can to prevent that
OL,12,Finformation coming out," she said.
OL,14,FMr Benn had brought the case to the
OL,15,FCourt of Appeal to challenge an
OL,16,Fearlier ruling by a High Court judge
OL,17,Fthat he must set up a public inquiry
OL,18,Finto the killing.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@XO]
