OL,3,C'No surprise, just disappointment,'
OL,4,Csay Brown family over Benn inquiry
OL,5,Cappeal
OL,7,FThe Secretary of Statement contends
OL,8,Fthe case involves a key constitutional
OL,9,Fprinciple of who should order public
OL,10,Finquiries, the Government or the
OL,11,Fjudiciary.
OL,13,FIn regard to Mr Brown's murder, Mr
OL,14,FBenn argues the case could instead be
OL,15,Fdealt with by a new Troubles
OL,16,Finvestigatory body, the Independent
OL,17,FCommission for Reconciliation and
OL,18,FInformation Recovery (ICRIR).
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G12/15
