OL,3,C'No surprise, just disappointment,'
OL,4,Csay Brown family over Benn inquiry
OL,5,Cappeal
OL,7,FLast year, a coroner halted an inquest
OL,8,Finto the killing, expressing concern
OL,9,Fthat his ability to examine the case
OL,10,Fhad been "compromised" by the extent
OL,11,Fof confidential state material being
OL,12,Fexcluded from the proceedings on
OL,13,Fnational security grounds.
OL,15,FThe Court of Appeal judges said the
OL,16,Flimitations of the ICRIR to deal with
OL,17,Fcases such as Mr Brown's killing are
OL,18,F"apparent".
OL,26,@rD@JOUrD@VO]zD@AOUzD@JO]
