OL,3,C'No surprise, just disappointment,'
OL,4,Csay Brown family over Benn inquiry
OL,5,Cappeal
OL,7,FThe panel of judges said the
OL,8,Fcommission, as it is currently
OL,9,Festablished, is not equipped to deal
OL,10,Fwith cases which involve sensitive
OL,11,Fmaterial.
OL,13,FMr Benn has vowed to implement reforms
OL,14,Fto ensure the new truth recovery body
OL,15,Fis capable of carrying out an
OL,16,Findependent and rigorous investigation
OL,17,Finto the murder of Mr Brown.
OL,19,FThe ICRIR was established as part of
OL,20,Fthe previous government's contentious
OL,21,FLegacy Act.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G14/15
